To run:

$ bin/Grider.exe

When prompted, set the viewer path or leave it to the default value.
Grider works with both the standard Linden viewer and others (e.g. Hippo).

- As first name enter First.Last
- As last name enter the address of your user server. For example:
  localhost:9000
  osgrid.org
- As password, enter your password

Grider requires a grid supporting HG2.
